Please!

00:38.044 --> 00:40.023
I'm sorry, Geoffrey.

00:40.024 --> 00:42.044
I'm not the man for this. Michael...

00:42.045 --> 00:43.072
I can't do it!

00:46.060 --> 00:47.091
I'm sorry.

00:47.092 --> 00:50.062
Wait! Michael...
I'll find you someone else.

00:50.063 --> 00:53.024
Just tell me what happened.
Thank you, Alice.

01:02.084 --> 01:04.052
Oh, it'll be all right.

01:12.489 --> 01:33.572
